\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 We had only the two rooms in that. Only two. But - we had a wee }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5404307\charrsid8538783 offshoot}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783  at side where - th
ey - we could lay down - and there - and there - and there were a sitting room, there were a sitting room, you could lay down in a place outside. But the - the annexe on the house, you could lay down \{BLANK\}
 about six, I believe it would have held six. But I don't know how many exactly - be telling you a lie if I said there was six in it, but it would have held six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 And your parents would sleep in yet another room would they?
