\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you ever have any tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
Oh yes, oh tinned - if it was really rough, yes, we'd tinned meat, but not very much really. More so fresh meat, most of all fresh meat. Mother didna believe in tinned meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you ever get any extra meat from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
From poaching? No. Don't say we were goody-goody, we still poached a wee bit, still did a wee bit of poaching but - you couldnae call it - a regular supply, it was \{BLANK\} You know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Would you go poaching yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
Aye. Oh I caught an odd hare now and again but - but the - that was just a game for you you know, it wasnae - wansa - wasna a feed I would - a feed - we didna go and do it personally for eating. You went down to it for fun really. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
