Oh aye, oh you got presents right enough, when they - they were able to afford them you see. In fact that was a thing I ignored at that time, presents. Presents were nothing. Nowadays see - och I would say - presents as
 presents wouldn't come in until I would be what - about sixteen. Previous to that there was nothing at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 It wasn't customary?
