n, because there was nothing else at that time. Yes, it was horsedrawn. Horsedrawn hearse. A hearse they called it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you wear black?
