The women wore black mournings, yes, they'd mournings for - right away. So - so had everyone if they could afford it. Pretty often }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8212307\charrsid8538783 whether}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
 they could afford it or not they just got them. Yes, they - they - that's one thing they believed in, heavy mournings - at that day, oh quite - quite later on than that too. Oh aye.
