Oh there were nae visiting. You stayed in a way - well, you just - you didna stray far away you know when you went out. There werenae so much visiting then as there is nowadays, oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 You wouldn't go and see friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
No, not at all, not at all. You see the - you mostly - you stay in a wee village, you see {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 was a wee village at this time that we're talking about, it was only - a - a wee village, oh aye.
