\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8212307\charrsid8538783 s easy. Oh aye, because y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
ou - you just take your book over and put it in a box, you see, and - and - they pile it up in a - in a box and then you come out in your turns so there w
as no arguing about turns or anything, see, you'd to wait your name being - being called out, they called out, they took the - each book from the bottom and they called out your name, then you went up to the counter and you - gave your order. Oh aye, it w
as quite a good idea. There were no ar - no arguing about turns or anything you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Was this in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
