{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 And the same in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, the shop wasnae that far from the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 You were sent to do the messages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 On a - on a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8212307\charrsid8538783  Saturday - Sat - first thing y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
ou would do in a Saturday was twelve loafs. And then you - you had fourteen pound of sugar. This is all getting ready for you, to where you took the loafs, and - and things are - then you'd fourteen pound of sugar, couple of stone of po
tatoes and - oh there were nae quarters or half quarters or ounce - ounces the way there are nowadays, oh no. It was all big stuff. See, they were big families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Where did you used to go shopping in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 In Glasgow, well at the Co-operative. 
Yes. And - a wee - there was a wee shop - you're no supposed to give names, there was a grocers shop - just - up at the Cross, with - it was a big big long shop, oh - bigger than my shop you see nowadays, a long shop. Well you did go to shop there too. Ay
e
. It was - it was fancy shopping you did there. If you knew the boy you see you could always get a wee bit of skim - oh - 'cos - like used to get a - a stone of potatoes you see, you could go to him and - tell him to give - you - three stone of potatoes y
ou see. Well that was tuppence, the skim you would have off the mother.
