With - with my father? Yes, oh aye, I was out every Saturday with my father, I had to go and watch him. Had to go and watch dad. Of
 a Saturday, oh aye. Take him home. When he got a couple of - whenever he got in a couple or three pints I used to say, dad - oh that what was me mum's instructions you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 She used to send you?
