here, bring him home. Just used to go over and say, dad. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8212307\charrsid8538783 Right}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
, Jim, I'll be out in a minute. Away you went, just like that. Just like a wee angel.
