Oh it was lovely, we - we could - we - we thoroughly - and then - then if you waited too long - at night, and - this was an understanding with mum too - if we waited too long, if we weren't in - the house by eight o'clock she knew you weren't coming. You
 just stayed out the night. Whichever farm house you were in the night - aye, you just slept in the barn. Yes, well - you - obviously there was only one farm there, there were four or five farms there you see. You just bed down in the barn and - there you
 are, get away. Ready for trailing home the next morning. Oh there were no - there were nae roads or anything, no, no. It was in the hill.
