lp we could give her it was just - it wouldna be very much, when we were young I mean. No. Oh we all did our turn. But we were - we were lucky in a way again, we just have been a lucky family, I tell you I was lucky - we were lucky already. Well we'd two 
aunts had no children. Oh they were gems. Oh great. They were great.
