Well there was an odd one now and again, but - it was - there was - there was children that - are backward, y
ou understand. Were backward, and - they didn't know how to treat them, they were no teachers to treat them at that time - for backward children. The result is that they were just left at the mercy - of the children in their own age and believe me it wasn
a very much mercy they got. Because you canna get any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4529087\charrsid8538783 crueller}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
 than kiddies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 How old were you when you were too big to go to Glengarnock school?
