 was an up to date business, oh aye. Well the one at Glengarnock was up to date, it was just a new school when I was at it, aye, it was just newly made, it was just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4529087\charrsid8538783 newly made}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783  at Glengarnock, it's there yet as a matter of fact. Aye.
