And water. Oh, if - if there was any farm houses near handy we were all right, you could always go in and get - buttermilk or some
thing. Oh aye. Fill you a big - jug of buttermilk from a farm. Oh you'd plenty - as far as that was concerned - that was easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you like Troon?
