Well there was - there was some - some boys got let outside. Naughty boys, and - oh there was one or two naughty girls got left out too. But after \{BLANK\} that was all right, you know, they would maybe - that's going very slow now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 At the Troon school did the other children come from similar homes to yours?

