roon school, if you understand me again - was an aris - an aristocratic school. It is yet. You see - Troon - was what they called - a millionaires town. At that time. It practically is that yet. More millionaires in Troon than there is any other place in 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Britain{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, per square mile. So you know it would be better class children - in there. The - the better better - ones at that time, of course they could come into {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}. Come in much easier now, because there's plenty of transport now, there werenae much transport then. That going very slow, is it going all right? Aye.
