Oh sometimes you hadn't to do very much. Sometimes you just could make a - you see, a - heinous offence - was to be wrong in a sum. When I was - oh - in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} you know, aye, that was - that was terrible that. To be wrong in a sum. After you'd been taught.
