ou see. Others would be - joiners, carpenters. Oh all classes - some - some - some - it's a - it's a - a - it's a word I hate to use is la - a labourer. But the most of them would be coming from labouring homes as you would say. You understand. It didnae 
m
atter how they lived - the - the - the mother was working - now where their mother went there they were working in the mills. You see, and - may have been - earning more wages than their man. But the combined wages would - were good, way above the ordinar
