kward children. And they - they were taken away, just as they're taken away just now only - it's a - it's a fancy word they call - they call them now, at that time it was a horse and cart or something like that you know. They were taking a few away to - t
o these special schools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Were there any gangs or groups in the Glastow school?
