ill ganging but - but there was none of this bottle stuff that you get now and razor stuff, you know, that was - you used your fists. Just fight with their fists you know. No bottles or razors or - nothing like that at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Were there any children who were left out of things?
