were just no class. The girls had to be good at - well, you know all the womens sports, the men - men is the same. You had to be good at some of these things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 And if they weren't good were they left out of things?
