Well, these were pretty good hours there. You - he wasnae too particular with you - Monday, Tuesday, Wednesd
ay, Thursday. Just wanted as many time to you on Sat - Friday and Saturday you had to be in -t nine o'clock, prompt. And Saturday, you'd to be in a nine o'clock prompt but you got a half day off on Saturday. Finished at four o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 When did you normally finish during the week?
