Well I was pretty good in that - that job because - I had - I had twenty-two shillings a week - and a bonus, a bonus for the - whatever I sold myself. You see what I m
ean - although I was book keeping, that wasnae occupying all my time, so sometimes I went into the shop and give them a wee - wee heave with the shop, well - if - if I got in and I sold a suit - you see, I got a bonus for that. Aye.
