ave been the Sunday school, it might have been at a - a - a Raccobite meeting or - or something that - or it may have been a - it may have been a - a music - music - see we still kept on - with music at the school. There wasnae much music attached to it b
ut we were still learning, you know. Well the - that's where you met quite a few. There.
