 shoes came from Uncle Jim. He - he - he didnae make them specially. The likes of me or dad he made them specially for us you know, measured you and made them. But the others, it was just - I think he was buying them in, the cheap quality, buying them in 
from the Jews or something. But - but I don't know that, I'm just - saying I think that.
