Oh - oh yes, oh - oh you - you couldnae keep them back from meeting - meeting them because they - they made themselves known.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
