At - at that time she came from Toll Cross but she actually was born in Ayrshire. She was born in a place called Gorls - although she lived all her life in - she - she'd been in - I would say, her fa
ther got killed in the pits. And - after he got his compensation whatever it was, the mother came to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 then. Quite young. And she opened a fish and tatty shop. You see, it was the money she had got - well - that's like - she was the fourth in the family, well - she must have been very young when she came to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. She couldn't have been very old. Mm. She - she'd been a long while in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 when I met her you understand, she - oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you save money before getting married or not?
