 - you started to save when you made up your mind to - but you - you'd no money to - otherwise all the money went to your mum you see. But we - were going to get married or thinking about getting married, you told her and she said oh we'll need to get sta
rted in a bank then James. And - get two or three shillings or a pound. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Would she save it for you?
