Oh - oh that was - when would that be, 19 - 20 - wait 'til I get this all fixed up, now 1914 - 1919. 1919. About 1923. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 How old was your wife when you got married?
