No. Well - oh aye, wait a minute now. Wait a minute now, be - before - well she was a weaver from she left school. But
 before she left school she had a wee odd job. It was - aye - going with - with the papers or something. They all did something, the kiddies at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13717364\charrsid8538783 that}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783  time, barring me, my dad wouldna allow any of us do anything. No - that's right, no, she never did anything
 at all - bar weaving. She went in and learned the weaving and - that's where she was 'til she got married.
