ife didn't eat many vegetables now you - now you're bringing that up, she didn't take many vege - veg - vegetables. Didn't - didn't take very many potatoes or anything. But - the - but all the other things - any other vegetables you could - make nice - yo
u could get it out the fields, you know, yes.
