Oh aye, oh they'd presents. And all the - the wee knick-knacks you used to put in the dumpling and all that sort of thing you know, aye. Oh - all the fun of the fair. Treacle scones and all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did they have friends round?
