\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Oh aye, it used to be m
urder. My wife used to day, oh I wish there would be no more or these birthdays, she - she says, they're terrible, so - so it was. Maybe had - couple of dozen of youngsters, just dong what they liked you know what I mean because it was - after all's said 
it was a birthday party. You couldna keep running about - checking them all the time, you'd to let them have their - let them have their got.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
Was this from the very first child, even when your very first little boy was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Ah well you see, if 
you - if you had a birthday - even when mine was young - although I was the oldest in the family right enough, but - but it's unique just for - for - the likes of me to be the first in a family, and none of the others are have any children. You - you see,
 it - it - it was a unique thing in our house. Me being the oldest and then none - but most all families have always got two or three or so. See? Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 
