Well - no, not - not on Christmas Day, they just took what they got for Christmas Day I expect. But - before Christma
s - you always took them in town, Oh aye. OH you took them in town took - took them all round the different shops. They thoroughly enjoyed that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you have any musical instruments in your house?
