\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 What about your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16601601 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Well sh
e could play, aye, she could play. Young son can play. The rest of us could make a real noise on occasion, but I'm talking about real playing. The youngster was a smashing player. I think he should have been, it cost plenty to - educate him. He was educat
e
d to it. My - my - my wife, she was just - she was just a - hand player you know, she's - she had - she had been at lessons right enough but they didn't do her much good, she never was long enough at them. But - as a - as an ear player she took a bit of b
eating, she was very good at ear playing, oh aye, just was champion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did any of you sing?
