Oh they went out with me pretty often. Oh aye. You went away for a rest. That's what it was really, for - you could take him out for to give - the wife a rest.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 What did you do on Bank Holidays?
