Well - when - when - due - before we went to war - saw him about - you'd see him every - night, you see, we worked night work and - and day shift you see at the - so actually - we were both
 in the same shift so - it was just a matter of - of whatever - if you were - if we were night shift - didn't see him - at all that week. But the next week you'd see him - see him every night. See?
