Oh well, as I tell you - we - we - we - we'd quoits - qoit - you know quoits. That - that was a summer game
, that was for outside. And - and bowls. Bowling. A bowling alley, in - in the wintertime of course you - you were inside playing draughts, dominoes and - and etcetera, etcetera, etcetera, you know, various other - indoor amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14641693 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2906979\charrsid8538783 Did you ever make music?
